WPILIB LabVIEW Math version 3.07 has been released. It can be found on github at the link below. The resources section of the LabVIEW Getting Started page also points to this repository.

Added functionality

  • Field and element display VIs. This allows field and moving robot to be displayed on a dashboard or separate utility program. An example is provided under LabVIEW “Find Examples”
  • Additional Ramsete Execute functions that greatly simplify using external odometry such as Pose Est 2, or Diff Odom 2.
GitHub
